The Auto button is [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/camcorder-reviewer/Camcorder_Reviewer-JVC_GR-D796_Review.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://www.camcorderreviewer.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/02/jvc-gr-d796-review.jpg" alt="JVC GR-D796 Review" align="left" />The <em>JVC GR-D796</em> digital camcorder is the ultimate user-friendly video recording device that has the ability to capture professional-looking shots. Features are abundant in this JVC camcorder but the system is remarkably simple to operate. Those who use the unit appreciate its compact design and lightweight construction as well as its ease-of-use.</p>
<p>The Auto button is a fine example of the GR-D796’s user-friendly features. This button allows users to switch between auto and manual modes in an instant. This is wonderful for anyone who wants to take advantage of advanced manual features combined with simple automatic functions.</p>
<p>Picture quality is amazing using this JVC video recorder. Three dimension noise reduction (3D NR) is a feature that delivers accurate noise reduction in the images. Users can expect a brilliant image that is colorful and sharp using this advance noise reduction feature.</p>
<p>The 3D NR function is further enhanced with other illumination features built into the digital camcorder. Auto illumination uses a built-in LED light to reflect extra light onto a subject in dim conditions. The LED light is automatically disengaged once the unit enters a well-lit area. This helps to save power in the system.</p>
<p>NightAlive is a light-boosting feature that works wonders in darker conditions. Users can expect bright, brilliant pictures even in low light using this feature. Color is rich and there are no distance limitations using the NightAlive illumination feature. This feature works well when the unit is in still or video modes.</p>
<p>The system is started once the LCD display is opened or when the viewfinder is pulled out. This allows users to take footage or still images in record time. Stick control is another great time-saving feature that allows users to navigate the system with one-finger control.</p>
<p>There are many other benefits offered by the JVC GR-D796 digital camcorder including picture effects and transition fading. This user-friendly camcorder offers everything consumers need to capture memories.</p>
