<p>One of the most appealing features offered by this JVC camcorder is 25x optical zoom and 1000x digital hyper zoom. The 25x optical zoom allows users to enlarge a subject up to 25 times without compromising the composition. The result is crystal clear images even when brought up close from a distance.</p>
<p>Users can also expect outstanding digital picture improvement using the JVC VHSC GR-SXM38 digital camcorder. This device is brimming with great editing and enhancement features that are certain to help create professional-looking footage. These features were not available on older models and they are welcomed additions to today’s cutting edge home video recording technology.</p>
<p>Digital picture improvement technology can be applied during each stage from the camera to the actual recording. This technology serves to maximize the overall quality of the images. Users can take advantage of the advanced enhancement features whether they are taking their very first footage or are seasoned home video recording enthusiasts.</p>
<p>The picture stabilizer is a fascinating feature offered by this JVC digital camcorder. This outstanding feature actually has the ability to recognize the operator’s unique way of handling the device and it accommodates to his individual camera-shake characteristics. This unit is truly customized to the individual.</p>
<p>Shaky pictures are virtually a thing of the past with the combination of the picture stabilizer and the unit’s Time Base Corrector (TBC). TBC is useful in eliminating jittery pictures during playback. Chroma Noise Reduction (CNR) takes out color noise and smears from the images. The overall result is shake-free images that boast crisp lines and brilliant colors.</p>
<p>There are a plethora of other outstanding features offered by the JVC VHSC GR-SXM38 digital camcorder. This device is certainly worth investigating.</p>
