<p>Users can take advantage of the plethora of features presented by this Panasonic Mini DV Palmcorder camcorder. The device records onto a Mini DV tape recording format. The system expediently records footage directly on to a Mini DV tape for convenience and quick results.</p>
<p>The system has an impressive image sensor that works wonders with both moving pictures and still images. The camcorder has 32x optical zoom and variable speed. The focal length is 2.3 – 73.6 millimeter and the filter diameter is 37 millimeters. The system boasts 35 mm film camera equivalent quality in still images.</p>
