<p>The SDR-H200 camcorder boasts professional-grade broadcast technology. Users can enjoy brilliant color and striking detail using this innovative device. The 3CCD system processes light through three distinct levels. This prevents any light loss that may happen on standard systems with a 1CCD system.</p>
<p>Users can expect lifelike images each and every time they use the device. The 3CCD system automatically produces realistic images wrought with intricate detail and striking colors. There is little wonder why the 3CCD system is the one chosen for professional broadcast cameras.</p>
<p>The Panasonic SDR-H200 Palmcorder camcorder promises extending recording so operators do not have to fret over using taking too much time. The unit is generously equipped with a 30GB hard drive that has the capacity to hold as much video data as roughly twenty-two digital video discs.</p>
<p>Users can expect to record up to twenty-seven hours of footage without changing the recording medium whether it is a tape, disc or another medium. This makes the SDR-H200 the ideal digital video camera for long trips or special occasions that call for full length footage.</p>
<p>This Panasonic camcorder is designed for movers and shakers in mind. The system is well equipped with optical image stabilization that ensures that footage will be smooth and crystal clear even in bumpy conditions and when using the zoom functions. This feature promises stunning, clear images even when shown on a big-screen television set.</p>
<p>There are many other features to consider including five brightness levels that can be adjusted to different lighting conditions. The Panasonic SDR-H200 Palmcorder camcorder has plenty more to offer.</p>
