      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://www.camcorderreviewer.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/02/jvc-gz-mg255-review.jpg" alt="JVC GZ-MG255 Review" align="left" />The <em>JVC GZ-MG255</em> Everio Hybrid Camera is an innovative home video recording device that is certain to turn heads. The unit is remarkably lightweight and compact. The system is very easy to use and the camcorder is overflowing with impressive features that are designed to help make home videos professional looking.</p>
<p>One of the biggest concerns that camera operators have is the possible sudden loss of power in the middle of a shoot. The system’s data battery allows users to check how much power is left in the system with the simple touch of a button. In an instant, the operator knows whether or not he has enough power to finish the shoot or whether he should charge the system.</p>
<p>Those who are certain that they will require extended battery life can opt for larger capacity batteries for an extra charge. The batteries with larger capacity obviously offer significantly more recording time but they do not take up significantly more space. Users can opt for more power without adopting a larger system.</p>
<p>The JVC GZ-MG255 hybrid camera offers superior low light performance that presents natural color and brightness even in dimly lit environments. The camera features 34x optical zoom that boasts superior magnification without distortion. Users can expect crystal clear, colorful images even when the subject brought up close.</p>
<p>Stick control is built into the unit for additional convenience. This feature allows users to take advantage of a four-way, one-finger control that is conveniently situated on the outer edge of the LCD screen. Users can access everything from the manual camera setting to the menu using this handy feature.</p>
<p>The Everio camcorder has a slot designed for SD memory cards. These cards have the capacity to store video and still images. Users can opt for SDHC memory cards for larger capacity and faster speed. The added memory devices can be purchased separately.</p>
<p>There are a plethora of other features offered by the JVC GZ-MG255 Everio Hybrid Camera. This home video recording device is certain to bring years of memories to life.</p>
