<p>The instruction manual lays out the groundwork for using the camcorder. With a little guidance even a novice can be capturing professional quality images and footage using this device. The instructions are clear and very well organized so beginners have a head start on their home video endeavors.</p>
<p>Recording and viewing are two processes that are very rewarding using the SC-DC173U digital camcorder by Samsung. This accessible system allows camera operators to take advantage of a flexible 4.3 and 16:9 viewing and recording system. This means that there is no guesswork when it comes to results.</p>
<p>The entire image is certain to be recorded no matter which screen format is used. This is because the unit records footage in widescreen format in the first place. There is no fear of losing any of the images even when they are viewed on high definition television with wide formatting.</p>
<p>The optional memory is another appealing feature offered by this Samsung digital camera. The unit has a memory card slot that offers the option of using an SD card or MMC flash memory for added storage and convenience. Users can record both still images and moving footage on the optional memory products.</p>
<p>The images collected on the SC-DC173U camcorder are well worth storing. This device boasts a powerful optical zoom that brings subjects up close without losing image quality. Blurred lines and lost colors are not a concern using this innovative recording device.</p>
<p>Images can also be printed directly from the camcorder with PictBridge. This feature works with a 2.0 cable that hooks up to a compatible printer for instant gratification.</p>
<p>There are many other great features to explore on the Samsung SC-DC173U digital camcorder. This is an ideal choice for novices and experts alike.</p>
